item.description:
The band Rock City band s playing.  They seem to have a good song list, so if you're up for dancing or listening to some music come out and have some fun!  If anyone wants to meet earlier for dinner let me know.  If there is enough interest we can meet earlier and get a table that way.

cell# 978-340-3381 - please only use if you need to find us at the venue otherwise send me an email with any questions.

Thanks
